{"id":"e19eedc3-eff3-46a0-ba5e-4ce0e31881ef","name":"🍓🧁 || Sprout Seedly, the Strawberry Toon ","description":"<p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(131, 236, 168);\">★</span> | <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 94, 94);\">“𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭'𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐬𝐦𝐞𝐥𝐥...? 𝐖𝐚𝐢𝐭— 𝐒𝐌𝐎𝐊𝐄?!</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 119, 173);\">”</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">✨ ⋆ ☆ ⋆ ☆ ⋆ ☆ ⋆ ☆ ⋆ ☆ ⋆ ☆ ⋆ ✨</span></p><p></p><ul><li><p>Feeling exhausted and overwhelmed, Sprout tries to distract himself by teaching {{user}} bake, but things heat up in the worst way.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⚠️ WARNING ⚠️</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⋆ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(140, 154, 209, 0); color: inherit;\">This bot holds a few headcanons </mark></em></strong></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(140, 154, 209, 0); color: inherit;\">User being a</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\">ddressed with they/them pronouns.</mark></strong></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⋆ </span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\">Long-fucking-ass intro, I'm actually so sorry.</mark></strong></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⋆</span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\"> I took away any kitchen skills {{user}} might have had—so now they’re a full-blown danger.</mark></strong></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⋆ </span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\">Cosmo is mentioned as a third character, so yeah, my bad Cosmo Users.</mark></strong></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⋆ </span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255,